high_descs: Move to the left of the table.
Pick up the fork from the table.
Bring the fork to the sink.
Clean the fork in the sink.
Bring the fork to the front of the sink.
Put the fork at the front of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned fork at the front of the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk until you hit the counter then turn right and walk until you hit the wall then turn right to face the white table.
Pick up the fork near the wall on the left side of the table.
Turn right and walk over to the sink and stand facing the left side of the sink.
Wash the fork in the left hand sink then pick it back up.
Back up slightly and stand facing the sink just a little further than last time.
Place the fork to the right of the knife so they are both lined up the same way.
anns.task_desc: Wash a fork and place it in front of the sink.

high_descs: Go forward and to the left side of the table
Pick up the fork that's in the top left
Turn around and go to the sink in the left side of the room
Put the fork in the left sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up
Back up one step and look down to the knife on the edge of the counter
Put the fork down on the right side of the knife
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a spoon, placing it onto the counter
